<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pricing | Teachures</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/base.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/components.css">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        .pricing-hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5rem 2rem 3rem;
        }

        .pricing-hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .toggle-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .toggle {
            width: 48px;
            height: 26px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 13px;
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
            border: none;
        }

        .toggle-knob {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: #F5C518;
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: absolute;
            top: 3px;
            left: 3px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .plans-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem 0 6rem;
        }

        .plan-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .plan-card:hover {
            border-color: rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .plan-card.featured {
            background: rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.04);
            border-color: rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.25);
        }

        .plan-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: -14px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #F5C518;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            padding: 4px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .plan-name {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: #F5C518;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .plan-price {
            font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 4rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #fff;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .plan-period {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .plan-desc {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }

        .feature-list li svg {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            color: #F5C518;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .feature-list li.muted {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .feature-list li.muted svg {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }

        .plan-cta {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.9rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .plan-cta.primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F5C518, #D4AA00);
            color: #000;
        }

        .plan-cta.primary:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(245, 197, 24, 0.4);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .plan-cta.outline {
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .plan-cta.outline:hover {
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .faq-section {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem 6rem;
        }

        .faq-item {
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 1.5rem 0;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .faq-q {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .faq-q svg {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .faq-a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            display: none;
            font-size: 0.93rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

        <main>
            <div class="pricing-hero container">
                <p
                    style="color:#F5C518; font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:3px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
                    Transparent Pricing</p>
                <h1>Simple Plans.<br><span
                        style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#F5C518,#FFD700);-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;">No
                        Surprises.</span></h1>
                <p
                    style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:1rem; font-size:1.1rem; max-width:500px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;">
                    Start for free. Scale when ready. Cancel anytime.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="container">
                <div class="plans-grid">
                    <!-- Free Plan -->
                    <div class="plan-card">
                        <p class="plan-name">Starter</p>
                        <div class="plan-price">$0</div>
                        <p class="plan-period">forever free</p>
                        <p class="plan-desc">Perfect to explore and start your first course.</p>
                        <ul class="feature-list">
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Access 50+ free courses</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Community forum access</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Progress tracking</li>
                            <li class="muted"><i data-lucide="x"></i> Certificates of completion</li>
                            <li class="muted"><i data-lucide="x"></i> Premium courses</li>
                            <li class="muted"><i data-lucide="x"></i> Offline access</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/register" class="plan-cta outline">Get Started Free</a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Pro Plan -->
                    <div class="plan-card featured">
                        <span class="plan-badge">Most Popular</span>
                        <p class="plan-name">Pro</p>
                        <div class="plan-price">$29</div>
                        <p class="plan-period">per month</p>
                        <p class="plan-desc">Everything you need to learn fast and get certified.</p>
                        <ul class="feature-list">
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Access ALL 400+ courses</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Verified certificates</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Download for offline</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Priority support</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Gamification & badges</li>
                            <li class="muted"><i data-lucide="x"></i> Team management</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="/register" class="plan-cta primary">Start 14-Day Trial</a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Team Plan -->
                    <div class="plan-card">
                        <p class="plan-name">Teams</p>
                        <div class="plan-price">$79</div>
                        <p class="plan-period">per seat / month</p>
                        <p class="plan-desc">Built for organizations that take learning seriously.</p>
                        <ul class="feature-list">
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Everything in Pro</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Team analytics dashboard</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Custom course builder</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> SSO / SCIM integration</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> Dedicated account manager</li>
                            <li><i data-lucide="check"></i> SLA guarantee</li>
                        </ul>
                        <a href="mailto:sales@teachures.com" class="plan-cta outline">Contact Sales</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ -->
            <div class="faq-section">
                <h2
                    style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif; font-size:3rem; text-align:center; margin-bottom:2.5rem; letter-spacing:1px;">
                    FAQ</h2>

                <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <div class="faq-q">Can I cancel anytime? <i data-lucide="chevron-down"></i></div>
                    <div class="faq-a">Yes, absolutely. You can cancel your subscription at any time from your account
                        settings. No questions asked, no hidden fees.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <div class="faq-q">Is there a free trial? <i data-lucide="chevron-down"></i></div>
                    <div class="faq-a">Pro plans come with a 14-day free trial. No credit card required to start.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <div class="faq-q">Do certificates expire? <i data-lucide="chevron-down"></i></div>
                    <div class="faq-a">No. All Teachures certificates are issued permanently and include a verification
                        link that never expires.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                    <div class="faq-q">Can I become an instructor? <i data-lucide="chevron-down"></i></div>
                    <div class="faq-a">Yes! Register as a Trainer and start creating courses immediately. Earn revenue
                        on every enrollment.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
            <script>lucide.createIcons();</script>
            <script>
                function toggleFaq(el) {
                    const ans = el.querySelector('.faq-a');
                    ans.style.display = ans.style.display === 'block' ? 'none' : 'block';
                }
            </script>
</body>

</html>